[[span style="font-family: var(--decorative-font); font-size:300%"]]页眉与装饰字体为Papel Picado/新愚公沧桑体。[[/span]]

[[span style="font-family: var(--decorative-font); font-size:700%"]]$ / #
@ & : ?[[/span]]

